  "description": "A stunning panoramic view of a city nestled beside a large body of water, bathed in the vibrant hues of a sunset. The sky is a dramatic spectacle, transitioning from deep indigo and purple at the zenith to fiery oranges and reds near the horizon. A distinct band of golden light marks the meeting point of the sun and the water, creating a dazzling effect. Below, the city lights twinkle, contrasting with the darkening landscape. Silhouetted hills and mountains frame the distant horizon, adding depth to the composition. The foreground features dark trees providing a natural framing element. The overall impression is one of serene beauty and urban tranquility.",
